The [[Seattle Mariners]] took part in both the [[Major League Baseball]] [[Rule 4 draft]] but not the [[Rule 5 draft]] in {{mlby|2006}}.<ref name="cube"/>
The [[2006 Major League Baseball Draft]] was held from June 6 to 7.<ref name="cube">{{cite web |url=http://www.thebaseballcube.com/draft/2006/26.shtml |title=2006 Seattle Mariners Draft Picks |author= |date= |work=The Baseball Cube |publisher=thebaseballcube.com |accessdate=December 29, 2009}}</ref> The Mariners selected a total of 50 players in the draft. Of those 50 players, the Mariners signed 26 players.<ref name="cube"/> They did however sign multiple players after the draft deadline.
